Class SmartColorLamp

  • java.lang.Object
    • SmartDevice
      • SmartLamp
        • SmartColorLamp

  • public class SmartColorLamp
extends SmartLamp

    The SmartColorLamp class is represents a smart color lamp. It is a subclass of SmartLamp class. It's contains necessary methods and properties for a smart color lamp.
